/ service section
%section#sec3.service.text-left
  .container
    .row
      .service-overlay
      .col-md-12
        %h2 INFO
        = image_tag "chevrons.png"
        %p          
          The Citroen Rendezvous may be the largest gathering of Citroens 
          %br in North America, but above all, it is about the people. 
          We encourage you to bring friends and family, and we welcome 
          %br not just Citroens, but all French marques. In fact, we won't 
          turn you away, whatever you bring!
      .col-md-12.services
        .col-md-2.single-service.col-xs-6.col-sm-3
          %i.fa.fa-hotel
          %h3 Accommodations
          %p 
            Saratoga Springs is well known as a vacation destination and has a wealth of places to stay. Let the
            = link_to 'convention and tourism bureau', 'http://discoversaratoga.org/saratoga/lodging', { :target => '_blank' }
            be your guide, or use your favorite travel website.
        .col-md-2.col-md-push-1.single-service.col-xs-6.col-sm-3
          %i.fa.fa-shopping-cart
          %h3 Supporting Vendors
          %p 
            We couldn't put on the Rendezvous (nor could we keep our cars going) without our
            = link_to 'friendly and knowledgeable supporting vendors', '/vendors'
      .col-md-12.services.bottom-services
        .col-md-2.single-service.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
          %i.fa.fa-calendar
          %h3 History
          %p 
            Lance Hellmann, one of the original organizers of the Rendezvous has kindly written a 
            = link_to 'charming little history', '/history'
            of the event. Enjoy!
        .col-md-2.col-md-push-1.single-service.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
          %i.fa.fa-empire
          %h3 Organization
          %p Onsectetur adipisicing elit, sedo eiusmod tempor incidiet dolorerserss eerhfre mag.
/ about section ends
/ portfolio section
%section#sec4.portfolio.text-center
  .row.portfolio-row
    .portfolio-heading
      %h2 PHOTOS
      = image_tag "chevrons.png"
      %p
        The best things about the Rendezvous are the cars and the people!
    - if @pictures.count == 8 
      - @pictures.each do |pic|
        .col-md-3.single-portfolio.col-sm-6
          %figure.portfolio-item
            = image_tag pic.image.portfolio.url + @cache_buster, :class => 'img-responsive'
            %figcaption.portfolio-details
              %h4= pic.caption
              %p= pic.credit
          %a{:href => pic.image.url}
            %i.fa.fa-search
    - else
      - (1..8).each do |n|
        .col-md-3.single-portfolio.col-sm-6
          %figure.portfolio-item
            = image_tag "portfolio#{n}.jpg", :class => 'img-responsive'
            %figcaption.portfolio-details
              %h4 Photo #{n}
              %p Placeholder photo
          %a{:href => "portfolio#{n}.jpg"}
            %i.fa.fa-search
/ end of portfolio section
